reviewText:
Three young Native Americans decide to abduct a land-mogul's daughter when the wealthy land developer swipes tribal acreage. Exposed to the "other side," this young woman finds herself joining the side of her abductors.

Rating: Not Rated
Runtime: 1 hr 35 mins
Genre: Crime
Director: Paul Leder
Cast: Barbara Bosson, Sondra Currie, Leslie Hope, Bernie White
